A towering golden throne made entirely of stacked coins and currency from various nations, sitting atop a steep pyramid of smaller bronze and silver coins, with tiny silhouetted figures climbing the pyramid's sides trying to reach the top. The scene is set against a dramatic sunset sky with deep oranges and purples. At the base of the pyramid, a vast crowd of miniature people stretches to the horizon. The composition emphasizes the extreme height disparity between the opulent throne and the ground level. Style: Vintage propaganda poster aesthetic with muted sepia tones, bold geometric shapes, and art deco influences reminiscent of 1930s political artwork.
